flowchart LR
    U[用户]
    V[访客]
    OA[组织管理员]
    SA[系统管理员]

    subgraph Client[前端客户端 Vue3]
        C1[页面视图 Views]
        C2[路由 Router]
        C3[状态管理 Pinia]
        C4[API请求 Axios]
        C5[实时通知 Socket.io Client]
        C6[富文本编辑器 Tiptap]
    end

    subgraph Server[后端服务 Node.js + Express]
        S1[路由层 Routes]
        S2[中间件 Middleware\n认证/权限/审计]
        S3[业务服务层 Services]
        S4[工具层 Utils]
    end

    subgraph DB[数据与资源层]
        D1[(MySQL)]
        D2[(附件存储 Uploads)]
        D3[WebSocket推送]
    end

    U --> C1
    V --> C1
    OA --> C1
    SA --> C1

    C1 --> C2
    C1 --> C3
    C1 --> C4
    C1 --> C5
    C1 --> C6

    C4 --> S1
    C5 --> D3

    S1 --> S2
    S2 --> S3
    S3 --> S4
    S3 --> D1
    S3 --> D2
    S3 --> D3

    D3 --> C5
